39:28.000 --> 39:30.000
Abigail Cross is burning.

39:30.000 --> 39:31.000
Yes!

39:31.000 --> 39:32.000
Says Nick.

39:32.000 --> 39:34.000
And the other ghosts are burning too.

39:34.000 --> 39:36.000
Look! The door is opening.

39:36.000 --> 39:37.000
Says Bill.

39:37.000 --> 39:39.000
Quick! Let's go!

39:39.000 --> 39:42.000
Everyone runs outside.

39:42.000 --> 39:44.000
Bill carries.

39:45.000 --> 39:47.000
Everyone runs outside.

39:47.000 --> 39:49.000
Bill carries Kelly outside.

39:49.000 --> 39:51.000
Is everyone here?

39:51.000 --> 39:53.000
