40:21.000 --> 40:22.000
I don't know!

40:22.000 --> 40:24.000
Answers Bill.

40:24.000 --> 40:26.000
Everyone is standing near Kelly.

40:26.000 --> 40:28.000
Oh Kelly, please wake up.

40:28.000 --> 40:30.000
Says Megan.

40:30.000 --> 40:32.000
Suddenly, it starts raining.

40:32.000 --> 40:35.000
There is thunder and lightning.

40:35.000 --> 40:37.000
Kelly moves her head.

40:37.000 --> 40:38.000
Where am I?

40:38.000 --> 40:39.000
She asks.

40:39.000 --> 40:43.000
Oh Kelly, you're okay. I'm so happy.

40:43.000 --> 40:44.000
Says Megan.

40:44.000 --> 40:46.000
What's happening?

40:46.000 --> 40:48.000
Asks Kelly.

40:48.000 --> 40:52.000
Bill smiles and explains everything to her.

40:52.000 --> 40:54.000
Do you believe in ghosts now?

40:54.000 --> 40:56.000
Asks Nick.

40:56.000 --> 40:58.000
Bill looks at him.

40:58.000 --> 41:00.000
And slowly says...

41:00.000 --> 41:02.000
Well...

41:02.000 --> 41:04.000
Yes.

41:09.000 --> 41:12.000
Then they all go home.

41:12.000 --> 41:16.000
Kelly has some strange dreams that night.

41:16.000 --> 41:19.000
The next morning she wakes up early.

41:19.000 --> 41:21.000
Megan is still sleeping.

41:21.000 --> 41:24.000
She is happy to be home.

41:24.000 --> 41:27.000
She gets up and goes to the bathroom.

41:27.000 --> 41:32.000
She looks in the mirror and cannot believe her eyes.

41:32.000 --> 41:34.000
What can she see?

41:34.000 --> 41:37.000
A red mark around her neck.

41:37.000 --> 41:40.000
A mysterious voice in the mirror says...

41:40.000 --> 41:45.000
When you play with fire, Kelly, you burn your fingers.

41:52.000 --> 41:56.000
Suddenly, the decorations on the wall start moving.

41:56.000 --> 41:59.000
The bats are flying around the room.

41:59.000 --> 42:02.000
They are making strange noises.

42:02.000 --> 42:03.000
No!

