Screams a girl.

42:04.000 --> 42:06.000
There's a bat in my hair!

42:06.000 --> 42:07.000
Help!

42:07.000 --> 42:08.000
Screams a boy.

42:08.000 --> 42:10.000
This bat is a vampire!

