A candle on the table falls.

42:40.000 --> 42:43.000
The paper table cloth is burning.

42:43.000 --> 42:44.000
Fire!

42:44.000 --> 42:45.000
We must get out of here.

42:45.000 --> 42:47.000
It says Bill.

42:47.000 --> 42:49.000
Oh no, it's a big fire.

42:49.000 --> 42:51.000
It says Susan.

42:51.000 --> 42:52.000
We can't open the door.

42:52.000 --> 42:53.000
It says Nick.

42:53.000 --> 42:54.000
It's five to midnight.

42:54.000 --> 42:57.000
At midnight, the ghosts take our bodies.

42:57.000 --> 42:59.000
What can we do?

42:59.000 --> 43:01.000
I must find Kelly.

